detail.name: Vegeta (Mini) : DA
detail.effect:
[Permanent][Your Turn] If you have 7 or fewer cards in your hand, this card gets +5000 power.
[When Attacking] Choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards and reduce its cost by 2 for the turn.

detail.name: ベジータ(ミニ)：DA
detail.effect: 【永続】【自分のターン中】自分の手札が7枚以下の場合、このカードのパワー+5000。【アタック時】相手のバトルカード1枚までを選び、このターン中、コスト-2。
